1
00:00:06,667 --> 00:00:09,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Your name is Lee Hyun Woo. You graduated Seoin Elementary School.</font>

2
00:00:10,097 --> 00:00:12,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Your brother Lee Sang Woo always waited for you...</font>

3
00:00:12,027 --> 00:00:14,497
<font color=#FFFF00>in the schoolyard until you got dismissed.</font>

4
00:00:15,327 --> 00:00:17,497
<font color=#FFFF00>You were a good student who was kind and polite.</font>

5
00:00:17,527 --> 00:00:19,627
<font color=#FFFF00>He adored his little brother very much.</font>

6
00:00:20,127 --> 00:00:23,367
<font color=#FFFF00>After his father who used to drive a school bus wrongfully died,</font>

7
00:00:23,367 --> 00:00:25,027
<font color=#FFFF00>he and his brother were sent to an orphanage.</font>

8
00:00:25,897 --> 00:00:29,497
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo was adopted, and his little brother went missing.</font>

9
00:00:31,067 --> 00:00:32,427
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing right now?</font>

10
00:00:32,697 --> 00:00:35,037
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a story about a man I know.</font>

11
00:00:36,327 --> 00:00:38,927
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, that Lee Hyun Woo guy...</font>

12
00:00:39,567 --> 00:00:41,467
<font color=#FFFF00>moved to our town six months ago.</font>

13
00:00:42,167 --> 00:00:43,227
<font color=#FFFF00>And he happened to live...</font>

14
00:00:44,467 --> 00:00:48,797
<font color=#FFFF00>right across from the man who was related to his father's death.</font>

15
00:00:51,667 --> 00:00:52,867
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you come here?</font>

16
00:00:55,297 --> 00:00:56,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you come to take revenge?</font>

17
00:01:03,367 --> 00:01:04,927
<font color=#FFFF00>This is really funny.</font>

18
00:01:06,627 --> 00:01:09,737
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess you've finished reading that lousy romance novel.</font>

19
00:01:10,267 --> 00:01:11,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Now you're writing a detective story.</font>

20
00:01:11,997 --> 00:01:14,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop being sarcastic and just answer my questions.</font>

21
00:01:15,127 --> 00:01:16,127
<font color=#FFFF00>So what's next?</font>

22
00:01:16,867 --> 00:01:21,167
<font color=#FFFF00>So that Hyun Woo returned to the town he lived...</font>

23
00:01:21,297 --> 00:01:24,427
<font color=#FFFF00>and dated Jeong Eun and walked away to take revenge for his father?</font>

24
00:01:24,727 --> 00:01:27,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you saying you were dumped for nothing...</font>

25
00:01:27,227 --> 00:01:28,827
<font color=#FFFF00>but revenge?</font>

26
00:01:30,267 --> 00:01:32,827
<font color=#FFFF00>If that sounds to be an acceptable reason for our breakup,</font>

27
00:01:33,727 --> 00:01:35,167
<font color=#FFFF00>you can think that way.</font>

28
00:01:36,727 --> 00:01:38,767
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what I want to say to you.</font>

29
00:01:39,867 --> 00:01:42,227
<font color=#FFFF00>You're right. I haven't accepted the fact...</font>

30
00:01:42,267 --> 00:01:44,227
<font color=#FFFF00>we broke up.</font>

31
00:01:44,597 --> 00:01:48,567
<font color=#FFFF00>But you should know that I'm not here to beg and plead for your love.</font>

32
00:01:49,167 --> 00:01:51,497
<font color=#FFFF00>Why? That's not the real issue.</font>

33
00:01:51,497 --> 00:01:53,867
<font color=#FFFF00>You're in a more terrible fix.</font>

34
00:01:55,027 --> 00:01:57,897
<font color=#FFFF00>- What's the issue? - You should give up...</font>

35
00:01:59,367 --> 00:02:00,397
<font color=#FFFF00>on the revenge.</font>

36
00:02:02,097 --> 00:02:05,497
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know what you've done, and what you're about to do.</font>

37
00:02:05,767 --> 00:02:06,997
<font color=#FFFF00>But stop it.</font>

38
00:02:08,167 --> 00:02:09,197
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm begging you.</font>

39
00:02:09,797 --> 00:02:12,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Please don't, Hyun Woo.</font>

40
00:02:12,297 --> 00:02:14,667
<font color=#FFFF00>You might put yourself in danger instead.</font>

41
00:02:16,637 --> 00:02:17,637
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Eun,</font>

42
00:02:19,427 --> 00:02:22,297
<font color=#FFFF00>the first impression I've got from you turned to be right.</font>

43
00:02:22,997 --> 00:02:25,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Women who poke their nose into everything, make reckless guesses,</font>

44
00:02:26,267 --> 00:02:28,327
<font color=#FFFF00>and speak what's on their mind without thinking just like you.</font>

45
00:02:29,097 --> 00:02:30,497
<font color=#FFFF00>That's the type I hate the most.</font>

46
00:02:31,597 --> 00:02:35,027
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hyun Woo... - Let me tell you why I left you.</font>

47
00:02:35,727 --> 00:02:37,297
<font color=#FFFF00>This is the reason.</font>

48
00:02:37,697 --> 00:02:41,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Your such thoughtless behaviors put me under a lot of stress.</font>

49
00:02:41,797 --> 00:02:44,527
<font color=#FFFF00>But I tried to be nice to you until the last moment.</font>

50
00:02:45,067 --> 00:02:46,397
<font color=#FFFF00>You need to stop here.</font>

51
00:02:47,267 --> 00:02:49,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think you're a detective or something?</font>

52
00:02:49,927 --> 00:02:51,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know anything about me?</font>

53
00:02:51,867 --> 00:02:53,997
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess you've written a novel by yourself...</font>

54
00:02:54,367 --> 00:02:56,267
<font color=#FFFF00>with what I've told you before.</font>

55
00:02:56,567 --> 00:02:59,997
<font color=#FFFF00>I seriously need you to stop this.</font>

56
00:03:00,827 --> 00:03:02,627
<font color=#FFFF00>You're making sick of you.</font>

57
00:03:31,767 --> 00:03:32,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello.</font>

58
00:03:37,627 --> 00:03:39,327
<font color=#FFFF00>We've met before.</font>

59
00:03:42,397 --> 00:03:46,267
<font color=#FFFF00>- Have we? - Aren't you Anchor Han Jeong Hwa?</font>

60
00:03:48,667 --> 00:03:51,297
<font color=#FFFF00>- Do you know me? - Of course.</font>

61
00:03:52,067 --> 00:03:55,767
<font color=#FFFF00>There was a time when every man in Korea knew you.</font>

62
00:03:57,697 --> 00:04:01,567
<font color=#FFFF00>- I see. - Wait. I'm not done talking yet!</font>

63
00:04:11,567 --> 00:04:12,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir.</font>

64
00:04:14,397 --> 00:04:17,527
<font color=#FFFF00>Would you spare me some time later?</font>

65
00:04:17,697 --> 00:04:19,297
<font color=#FFFF00>I'd like to have dinner with you.</font>

66
00:04:20,497 --> 00:04:21,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

67
00:04:22,897 --> 00:04:23,997
<font color=#FFFF00>See you later.</font>

68
00:04:45,267 --> 00:04:47,697
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jeong Hwa. - Do you know him?</font>

69
00:04:51,067 --> 00:04:54,067
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, why are you coming out of this house?</font>

70
00:04:54,297 --> 00:04:57,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Well... It is because...</font>

71
00:04:57,397 --> 00:04:59,567
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, I delivered coffee.</font>

72
00:05:01,497 --> 00:05:02,527
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

73
00:05:03,267 --> 00:05:04,697
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jeong Hwa. - Right!</font>

74
00:05:05,167 --> 00:05:07,327
<font color=#FFFF00>I have to go meet my anchor friends.</font>

75
00:05:07,327 --> 00:05:08,597
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going to be a little late.</font>

76
00:05:09,067 --> 00:05:10,997
<font color=#FFFF00>If it's okay with you, please watch Ye Bin.</font>

77
00:05:11,937 --> 00:05:13,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa! Jeong Hwa!</font>

78
00:05:18,067 --> 00:05:19,997
<font color=#FFFF00>What is happening?</font>

79
00:05:20,167 --> 00:05:21,467
<font color=#FFFF00>This can't be happening.</font>

80
00:05:28,797 --> 00:05:32,097
<font color=#FFFF00>You met such an unusual girl.</font>

81
00:05:36,467 --> 00:05:37,767
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you talking about Han Jeong Hwa?</font>

82
00:05:38,067 --> 00:05:39,597
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm referring to Han Jeong Eun.</font>

83
00:05:41,127 --> 00:05:44,567
<font color=#FFFF00>She managed to get very close to your secret.</font>

84
00:05:44,997 --> 00:05:48,667
<font color=#FFFF00>I think we should finish our business here soon.</font>

85
00:05:51,797 --> 00:05:52,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Right.</font>

86
00:05:53,627 --> 00:05:54,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's get it done quickly.</font>

87
00:05:55,327 --> 00:05:56,527
<font color=#FFFF00>It's very tough for me,</font>

88
00:05:58,367 --> 00:05:59,597
<font color=#FFFF00>and I am exhausted.</font>

89
00:06:03,767 --> 00:06:07,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness, my one and only granddaughter is getting divorced.</font>

90
00:06:08,297 --> 00:06:09,497
<font color=#FFFF00>Wait.</font>

91
00:06:10,197 --> 00:06:14,167
<font color=#FFFF00>I should wear this on my head and stay in bed.</font>

92
00:06:14,797 --> 00:06:16,927
<font color=#FFFF00>I should put on a show.</font>

93
00:06:17,397 --> 00:06:20,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Only then, they will stop this nonsense.</font>

94
00:06:25,467 --> 00:06:26,497
<font color=#FFFF00>Elizabeth.</font>

95
00:06:27,027 --> 00:06:28,797
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong, Elizabeth? Goodness.</font>

96
00:06:35,697 --> 00:06:37,767
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it?</font>

97
00:06:42,067 --> 00:06:43,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Elizabeth.</font>

98
00:06:43,297 --> 00:06:45,367
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

99
00:06:46,327 --> 00:06:48,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you crying?</font>

100
00:06:52,097 --> 00:06:53,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, dear.</font>

101
00:07:00,767 --> 00:07:02,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry too much about Jeong Hwa.</font>

102
00:07:03,327 --> 00:07:05,497
<font color=#FFFF00>I will talk to her.</font>

103
00:07:05,727 --> 00:07:07,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you talk to James?</font>

104
00:07:08,227 --> 00:07:10,067
<font color=#FFFF00>He wasn't picking up his phone.</font>

105
00:07:13,567 --> 00:07:14,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey.</font>

106
00:07:15,427 --> 00:07:17,597
<font color=#FFFF00>What will we do?</font>

107
00:07:18,097 --> 00:07:21,397
<font color=#FFFF00>We are about to have a divorcee in our family.</font>

108
00:07:21,397 --> 00:07:23,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Why would you say that?</font>

109
00:07:23,797 --> 00:07:25,797
<font color=#FFFF00>I will do everything to stop her.</font>

110
00:07:25,897 --> 00:07:29,297
<font color=#FFFF00>She even packed up and moved to Korea. How can we stop her?</font>

111
00:07:29,827 --> 00:07:32,967
<font color=#FFFF00>It's because you've been...</font>

112
00:07:32,967 --> 00:07:34,967
<font color=#FFFF00>favoring Jeong Hwa since she was little.</font>

113
00:07:34,967 --> 00:07:37,867
<font color=#FFFF00>She never listens to what we say.</font>

114
00:07:40,167 --> 00:07:41,427
<font color=#FFFF00>It breaks my heart.</font>

115
00:07:43,027 --> 00:07:44,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Both Seong Sik and Jeong Hwa...</font>

116
00:07:45,227 --> 00:07:47,497
<font color=#FFFF00>are more like enemies than my own children.</font>

117
00:07:47,827 --> 00:07:50,267
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on and eat some.</font>

118
00:07:50,597 --> 00:07:51,667
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

119
00:07:51,867 --> 00:07:54,197
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't even have the strength to eat porridge.</font>

120
00:08:22,227 --> 00:08:24,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Can I talk to you for a while?</font>

121
00:08:29,267 --> 00:08:30,467
<font color=#FFFF00>What happened?</font>

122
00:08:31,327 --> 00:08:32,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Huh?</font>

123
00:08:34,127 --> 00:08:35,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

124
00:08:35,867 --> 00:08:38,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui's script didn't get selected.</font>

125
00:08:38,467 --> 00:08:40,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that why you spent the night together?</font>

126
00:08:42,627 --> 00:08:44,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if things didn't go well with her work,</font>

127
00:08:44,897 --> 00:08:47,297
<font color=#FFFF00>you shouldn't have done this. This is just unbelievable.</font>

128
00:08:48,397 --> 00:08:49,397
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

129
00:08:49,767 --> 00:08:51,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui was really disheartened.</font>

130
00:08:51,827 --> 00:08:53,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, I can't believe this.</font>

131
00:08:58,097 --> 00:08:59,427
<font color=#FFFF00>So where on earth...</font>

132
00:09:00,127 --> 00:09:02,067
<font color=#FFFF00>did you two go?</font>

133
00:09:03,127 --> 00:09:04,267
<font color=#FFFF00>We were at a library.</font>

134
00:09:04,397 --> 00:09:05,427
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

135
00:09:05,627 --> 00:09:06,667
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

136
00:09:09,127 --> 00:09:11,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Both Dong Hui and you...</font>

137
00:09:11,537 --> 00:09:13,867
<font color=#FFFF00>are unbelievable.</font>

138
00:09:14,327 --> 00:09:16,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Is everyone who makes dramas as strange as you two?</font>

139
00:09:17,067 --> 00:09:19,767
<font color=#FFFF00>I know that you work together and that you are in-laws,</font>

140
00:09:19,767 --> 00:09:23,067
<font color=#FFFF00>but before that, you are a man and a woman.</font>

141
00:09:23,297 --> 00:09:25,727
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you stay the night together?</font>

142
00:09:25,727 --> 00:09:27,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if Dong Hui was struggling,</font>

143
00:09:27,067 --> 00:09:29,397
<font color=#FFFF00>you should've brought her home.</font>

144
00:09:32,697 --> 00:09:34,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Do Mother and Father know about this too?</font>

145
00:09:34,867 --> 00:09:36,497
<font color=#FFFF00>No, they don't know this.</font>

146
00:09:38,297 --> 00:09:40,167
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with you, Seong Joon?</font>

147
00:09:40,167 --> 00:09:42,227
<font color=#FFFF00>This is very unlike you.</font>

148
00:09:49,397 --> 00:09:52,227
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it? Is there something you want to tell me?</font>

149
00:09:55,297 --> 00:09:56,537
<font color=#FFFF00>It's nothing.</font>

150
00:09:57,167 --> 00:09:58,467
<font color=#FFFF00>We shouldn't have done it.</font>

151
00:09:59,037 --> 00:10:00,097
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

152
00:10:37,267 --> 00:10:38,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo, stop. Stop.</font>

153
00:10:40,537 --> 00:10:43,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo, what did your teacher say about this song...</font>

154
00:10:43,467 --> 00:10:45,627
<font color=#FFFF00>during the last lesson?</font>

155
00:10:45,767 --> 00:10:47,127
<font color=#FFFF00>"Though Not Deserving".</font>

156
00:10:47,127 --> 00:10:50,267
<font color=#FFFF00>That's right. "Sebben, Crudele".</font>

157
00:10:50,767 --> 00:10:52,927
<font color=#FFFF00>"Though Not Deserving".</font>

158
00:10:53,467 --> 00:10:56,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if you don't deserve her,</font>

159
00:10:56,067 --> 00:10:58,267
<font color=#FFFF00>you will still love her.</font>

160
00:10:58,327 --> 00:11:00,367
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what the song is about, isn't it?</font>

161
00:11:00,697 --> 00:11:02,697
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes. - How should you sing it then?</font>

162
00:11:03,127 --> 00:11:05,527
<font color=#FFFF00>You should sing it more sorrowfully.</font>

163
00:11:06,297 --> 00:11:07,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay?</font>

164
00:11:08,097 --> 00:11:10,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Your lover doesn't love you.</font>

165
00:11:10,097 --> 00:11:12,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Cruelly, she refused your love.</font>

166
00:11:12,897 --> 00:11:15,767
<font color=#FFFF00>But you still love her.</font>

167
00:11:15,967 --> 00:11:17,267
<font color=#FFFF00>You want to keep loving her.</font>

168
00:11:17,267 --> 00:11:20,567
<font color=#FFFF00>How tragic is that?</font>

169
00:11:20,597 --> 00:11:21,967
<font color=#FFFF00>How should you sing it then?</font>

170
00:11:22,297 --> 00:11:23,967
<font color=#FFFF00>You have to...</font>

171
00:11:24,067 --> 00:11:27,027
<font color=#FFFF00>You have to be more emotional. Right?</font>

172
00:11:27,467 --> 00:11:29,267
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes. - Right.</font>

173
00:11:29,767 --> 00:11:31,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Now...</font>

174
00:11:32,527 --> 00:11:33,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are you going?</font>

175
00:11:34,927 --> 00:11:36,227
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going to my home. Why?</font>

176
00:11:36,967 --> 00:11:38,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Then listen to Chang Soo's song before you go.</font>

177
00:11:39,267 --> 00:11:41,927
<font color=#FFFF00>No, thanks. You should take care of your son.</font>

178
00:11:41,967 --> 00:11:43,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Aunt.</font>

179
00:11:44,697 --> 00:11:47,067
<font color=#FFFF00>- Did you just call me Aunt? - If you keep doing that to me,</font>

180
00:11:47,167 --> 00:11:50,227
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not going to visit you when I win a cash prize at a competition.</font>

181
00:11:50,397 --> 00:11:51,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey.</font>

182
00:11:52,267 --> 00:11:53,767
<font color=#FFFF00>When you win that prize,</font>

183
00:11:54,267 --> 00:11:56,597
<font color=#FFFF00>you should treat your mother.</font>

184
00:11:56,827 --> 00:11:59,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop bothering your aunt. Okay?</font>

185
00:12:00,397 --> 00:12:01,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Bye, Teacher.</font>

186
00:12:07,327 --> 00:12:10,867
<font color=#FFFF00>She doesn't have affection for her kids.</font>

187
00:12:11,027 --> 00:12:14,167
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why she's bad at bringing up her children.</font>

188
00:12:14,997 --> 00:12:17,867
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo, don't mind her. Just focus on your singing.</font>

189
00:12:18,567 --> 00:12:21,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Should we restart from the next bar?</font>

190
00:12:21,067 --> 00:12:22,597
<font color=#FFFF00>- Please play the piano. - Okay.</font>

191
00:12:22,627 --> 00:12:23,997
<font color=#FFFF00>- I got it. - Okay.</font>

192
00:12:32,627 --> 00:12:33,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Uncle.</font>

193
00:12:34,767 --> 00:12:35,767
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes?</font>

194
00:12:36,467 --> 00:12:37,527
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it, Ah In?</font>

195
00:12:38,067 --> 00:12:40,267
<font color=#FFFF00>Aren't you going to call Yoo Ra?</font>

196
00:12:45,127 --> 00:12:47,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Yoo Ra? Who is that?</font>

197
00:12:47,727 --> 00:12:49,397
<font color=#FFFF00>My friend Yoo Ra.</font>

198
00:12:49,467 --> 00:12:52,367
<font color=#FFFF00>You talked to her in the restroom the other time.</font>

199
00:12:52,997 --> 00:12:55,167
<font color=#FFFF00>She's...</font>

200
00:12:55,197 --> 00:12:57,697
<font color=#FFFF00>- She's no one... - Dad.</font>

201
00:12:58,167 --> 00:12:59,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop now.</font>

202
00:13:00,327 --> 00:13:02,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop what?</font>

203
00:13:03,167 --> 00:13:05,797
<font color=#FFFF00>I've read everything on the internet.</font>

204
00:13:05,927 --> 00:13:06,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey!</font>

205
00:13:07,397 --> 00:13:11,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Who told you to read things on the internet?</font>

206
00:13:11,097 --> 00:13:12,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Whatever. Just stop.</font>

207
