00:26:09,327 --> 00:26:10,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa.</font>

412
00:26:12,567 --> 00:26:15,127
<font color=#FFFF00>- Grandma. - Come here.</font>

413
00:26:16,867 --> 00:26:19,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it already. What time do you think it is? Give it to me.</font>

414
00:26:21,527 --> 00:26:22,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Give it back to me.</font>

415
00:26:22,997 --> 00:26:24,797
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll kill that jerk.</font>

416
00:26:24,797 --> 00:26:26,197
<font color=#FFFF00>He's a piece of trash.</font>

417
00:26:26,197 --> 00:26:29,127
<font color=#FFFF00>He's nothing but a scum, Dad.</font>

418
00:26:30,227 --> 00:26:32,297
<font color=#FFFF00>James, this is me.</font>

419
00:26:32,767 --> 00:26:35,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you know how late it is here?</font>

420
00:26:35,897 --> 00:26:36,967
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

421
00:26:37,167 --> 00:26:40,297
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't care what time it is there. This isn't right.</font>

422
00:26:40,297 --> 00:26:41,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Ask him...</font>

423
00:26:42,027 --> 00:26:44,297
<font color=#FFFF00>why we haven't been able to reach him.</font>

424
00:26:44,297 --> 00:26:45,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you really not know why?</font>

425
00:26:46,227 --> 00:26:48,427
<font color=#FFFF00>He couldn't contact us because he knew how shameful it is.</font>

426
00:26:48,427 --> 00:26:50,397
<font color=#FFFF00>How could he answer your calls...</font>

427
00:26:50,397 --> 00:26:53,127
<font color=#FFFF00>when he cheated on me and lived with another woman for three years?</font>

428
00:26:53,127 --> 00:26:54,197
<font color=#FFFF00>Stay quiet.</font>

429
00:26:57,167 --> 00:26:58,167
<font color=#FFFF00>James,</font>

430
00:26:58,897 --> 00:27:00,267
<font color=#FFFF00>let's call it a day.</font>

431
00:27:00,997 --> 00:27:03,967
<font color=#FFFF00>But I'll call you tomorrow. Make sure to answer it.</font>

432
00:27:05,167 --> 00:27:07,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Still, Ye Bin is here with her.</font>

433
00:27:07,197 --> 00:27:09,527
<font color=#FFFF00>You should've been more careful.</font>

434
00:27:10,027 --> 00:27:11,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Fine!</font>

435
00:27:12,267 --> 00:27:13,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop crying now.</font>

436
00:27:13,967 --> 00:27:15,997
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you crying so loud for?</font>

437
00:27:17,997 --> 00:27:19,627
<font color=#FFFF00>This is breaking my heart.</font>

438
00:27:24,567 --> 00:27:27,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Ye Bin, you should sleep next to me. Come here.</font>

439
00:27:29,427 --> 00:27:30,527
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

440
00:27:31,767 --> 00:27:33,197
<font color=#FFFF00>Ye Bin's dad is...</font>

441
00:27:33,767 --> 00:27:34,997
<font color=#FFFF00>seeing another woman.</font>

442
00:27:35,327 --> 00:27:37,527
<font color=#FFFF00>It's been more than three years.</font>

443
00:27:37,527 --> 00:27:39,897
<font color=#FFFF00>And we've been estranged for about two years.</font>

444
00:27:41,097 --> 00:27:43,897
<font color=#FFFF00>So how could I stay there any longer?</font>

445
00:27:44,997 --> 00:27:47,027
<font color=#FFFF00>This is so humiliating.</font>

446
00:27:49,497 --> 00:27:51,767
<font color=#FFFF00>I know. I understand.</font>

447
00:27:53,567 --> 00:27:54,667
<font color=#FFFF00>Still...</font>

448
00:27:55,467 --> 00:27:56,497
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry.</font>

449
00:27:56,867 --> 00:27:58,297
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure I'll win the divorce suit.</font>

450
00:27:58,967 --> 00:28:01,367
<font color=#FFFF00>It's him who caused us to get divorced.</font>

451
00:28:01,867 --> 00:28:03,197
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa,</font>

452
00:28:05,027 --> 00:28:07,227
<font color=#FFFF00>is it your turn this time?</font>

453
00:28:08,927 --> 00:28:10,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Your dad and I...</font>

454
00:28:11,127 --> 00:28:13,597
<font color=#FFFF00>cannot feel at ease for a day because of our children.</font>

455
00:28:15,397 --> 00:28:17,397
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm utterly exhausted now, Jeong Hwa.</font>

456
00:28:34,697 --> 00:28:35,727
<font color=#FFFF00>So?</font>

457
00:28:36,297 --> 00:28:37,667
<font color=#FFFF00>That's all.</font>

458
00:28:38,067 --> 00:28:39,597
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what happened.</font>

459
00:28:40,067 --> 00:28:42,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Is James insane?</font>

460
00:28:43,067 --> 00:28:44,897
<font color=#FFFF00>He seemed to be willing...</font>

461
00:28:44,927 --> 00:28:48,427
<font color=#FFFF00>to give her everything he had when he married her.</font>

462
00:28:48,427 --> 00:28:50,497
<font color=#FFFF00>How could he do this to her?</font>

463
00:28:50,527 --> 00:28:52,927
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what all guys are like, you know.</font>

464
00:28:53,127 --> 00:28:54,127
<font color=#FFFF00>So what is Jeong Ae doing?</font>

465
00:28:54,427 --> 00:28:56,597
<font color=#FFFF00>She got an IV at a clinic and fell asleep now.</font>

466
00:28:57,167 --> 00:29:00,827
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought Seong Sik's problem is finally settled.</font>

467
00:29:01,227 --> 00:29:04,127
<font color=#FFFF00>And it happened again.</font>

468
00:29:04,227 --> 00:29:05,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Where is Jeong Hwa?</font>

469
00:29:06,367 --> 00:29:08,127
<font color=#FFFF00>She shut herself in her room.</font>

470
00:29:08,567 --> 00:29:10,367
<font color=#FFFF00>What on earth is this?</font>

471
00:29:10,567 --> 00:29:13,567
<font color=#FFFF00>It's from smoke into smother.</font>

472
00:29:13,827 --> 00:29:17,567
<font color=#FFFF00>You know how disturbed I am. Please just leave.</font>

473
00:29:17,627 --> 00:29:18,727
<font color=#FFFF00>To where?</font>

474
00:29:18,767 --> 00:29:19,897
<font color=#FFFF00>To the third floor.</font>

475
00:29:20,067 --> 00:29:21,867
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't.</font>

476
00:29:22,297 --> 00:29:23,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Why not?</font>

477
00:29:23,297 --> 00:29:26,167
<font color=#FFFF00>There had been a big fuss because of Dong Hui the other day.</font>

478
00:29:26,167 --> 00:29:29,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Elizabeth cried so loudly.</font>

479
00:29:29,397 --> 00:29:32,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Because of Dong Hui? What happened to her?</font>

480
00:29:32,267 --> 00:29:34,127
<font color=#FFFF00>She slept out.</font>

481
00:29:34,197 --> 00:29:36,497
<font color=#FFFF00>- She slept out? - Yes.</font>

482
00:29:36,667 --> 00:29:39,467
<font color=#FFFF00>So Elizabeth gave her a good beating,</font>

483
00:29:39,467 --> 00:29:41,997
<font color=#FFFF00>even Hye Joo scolded her severely.</font>

484
00:29:41,997 --> 00:29:43,667
<font color=#FFFF00>It must have been chaotic.</font>

485
00:29:44,067 --> 00:29:46,327
<font color=#FFFF00>They kept it a secret from us.</font>

486
00:29:47,327 --> 00:29:49,867
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe that Dong Hui slept out.</font>

487
00:29:49,897 --> 00:29:52,927
<font color=#FFFF00>So that family is in a terrible mess too.</font>

488
00:29:53,467 --> 00:29:55,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui keeps apologizing,</font>

489
00:29:55,397 --> 00:29:56,927
<font color=#FFFF00>but Elizabeth doesn't bat an eye.</font>

490
00:29:56,927 --> 00:29:58,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

491
00:29:59,427 --> 00:30:02,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Why don't you stay on the first floor then?</font>

492
00:30:02,497 --> 00:30:05,067
<font color=#FFFF00>If you run into Jeong Hwa, you'll feel even more perturbed.</font>

493
00:30:05,097 --> 00:30:07,167
<font color=#FFFF00>But Chang Soo is singing loudly there.</font>

494
00:30:08,597 --> 00:30:11,897
<font color=#FFFF00>He sings all day long. It's too loud for me to stand.</font>

495
00:30:12,067 --> 00:30:14,067
<font color=#FFFF00>I can even hear him singing on the third floor.</font>

496
00:30:14,427 --> 00:30:15,527
<font color=#FFFF00>Dear me.</font>

497
00:30:16,067 --> 00:30:17,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Dear me.</font>

498
00:30:18,327 --> 00:30:20,567
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandma, I'm sorry.</font>

499
00:30:20,567 --> 00:30:22,397
<font color=#FFFF00>It won't happen again.</font>

500
00:30:24,327 --> 00:30:25,767
<font color=#FFFF00>Please forgive me.</font>

501
00:30:29,397 --> 00:30:30,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Then...</font>

502
00:30:31,127 --> 00:30:33,667
<font color=#FFFF00>please don't tell me to leave you.</font>

503
00:30:34,827 --> 00:30:36,297
<font color=#FFFF00>That makes me really sad.</font>

504
00:30:36,627 --> 00:30:39,727
<font color=#FFFF00>I have no one else than you.</font>

505
00:30:40,227 --> 00:30:41,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Please don't say that.</font>

506
00:30:44,467 --> 00:30:45,597
<font color=#FFFF00>You are...</font>

507
00:30:46,927 --> 00:30:48,667
<font color=#FFFF00>all I have.</font>

508
00:30:54,867 --> 00:30:57,427
<font color=#FFFF00>I will work hard today as I did.</font>

509
00:30:58,127 --> 00:31:00,027
<font color=#FFFF00>So please forgive me.</font>

510
00:31:03,667 --> 00:31:05,327
<font color=#FFFF00>I will see you after work.</font>

511
00:31:06,767 --> 00:31:08,197
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll come home early.</font>

512
00:31:43,027 --> 00:31:44,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Have some.</font>

513
00:31:44,897 --> 00:31:46,627
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not ill.</font>

514
00:31:46,627 --> 00:31:48,567
<font color=#FFFF00>I just lost my appetite.</font>

515
00:31:49,027 --> 00:31:51,067
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm just saying you should eat some porridge.</font>

516
00:31:51,267 --> 00:31:53,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if you don't eat, it won't solve anything.</font>

517
00:32:03,327 --> 00:32:04,427
<font color=#FFFF00>How is your grandmother?</font>

518
00:32:06,397 --> 00:32:08,827
<font color=#FFFF00>She doesn't even look at me.</font>

519
00:32:11,227 --> 00:32:14,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Please cheer up. This, too, shall pass away.</font>

520
00:32:14,767 --> 00:32:17,027
<font color=#FFFF00>I know. So I'll finish the next two episodes...</font>

521
00:32:17,027 --> 00:32:18,567
<font color=#FFFF00>by the end of this week.</font>

522
00:32:23,667 --> 00:32:24,697
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

523
00:32:25,727 --> 00:32:27,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Nothing.</font>

524
00:32:29,627 --> 00:32:30,627
<font color=#FFFF00>You look beautiful.</font>

525
00:32:31,127 --> 00:32:33,397
<font color=#FFFF00>You look better when you're energetic.</font>

526
00:32:35,427 --> 00:32:37,997
<font color=#FFFF00>I know. That's what makes me charming.</font>

527
00:32:40,397 --> 00:32:41,527
<font color=#FFFF00>Dig in.</font>

528
00:32:42,827 --> 00:32:46,227
<font color=#FFFF00>But I don't feel like eating porridge.</font>

529
00:33:12,127 --> 00:33:13,967
<font color=#FFFF00>How adorable.</font>

530
00:33:14,597 --> 00:33:16,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Please stop. We're not far from our office.</font>

531
00:33:16,967 --> 00:33:18,467
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll be fired if they see us.</font>

532
00:33:18,467 --> 00:33:19,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on.</font>

533
00:33:19,997 --> 00:33:22,567
<font color=#FFFF00>- How cute. - I said cut it out.</font>

534
00:33:22,567 --> 00:33:23,667
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going to be mad at you.</font>

535
00:33:23,967 --> 00:33:25,827
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't scare me at all.</font>

536
00:33:27,667 --> 00:33:29,267
<font color=#FFFF00>You have something on your face like a little kid.</font>

537
00:33:33,597 --> 00:33:34,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Eat up.</font>

538
00:33:39,767 --> 00:33:40,767
<font color=#FFFF00>It's tasty.</font>

539
00:34:00,597 --> 00:34:01,667
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop, Chang Soo.</font>

540
00:34:03,227 --> 00:34:06,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Teacher, I guess this is all for today.</font>

541
00:34:07,327 --> 00:34:09,427
<font color=#FFFF00>See you later. Take care.</font>

542
00:34:22,967 --> 00:34:23,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom,</font>

543
00:34:24,367 --> 00:34:25,497
<font color=#FFFF00>are you angry?</font>

544
00:34:25,727 --> 00:34:26,767
<font color=#FFFF00>I am not.</font>

545
00:34:28,497 --> 00:34:29,497
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

546
00:34:30,067 --> 00:34:31,097
<font color=#FFFF00>This is...</font>

547
00:34:32,867 --> 00:34:34,267
<font color=#FFFF00>not your issue.</font>

548
00:34:34,797 --> 00:34:35,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry?</font>

549
00:34:35,997 --> 00:34:37,427
<font color=#FFFF00>We need a new instructor.</font>

550
00:34:39,767 --> 00:34:41,897
<font color=#FFFF00>- You mean the instrumental teacher? - No,</font>

551
00:34:43,597 --> 00:34:45,067
<font color=#FFFF00>we need a new vocal teacher.</font>

552
00:34:46,397 --> 00:34:47,567
<font color=#FFFF00>Listen, Chang Soo.</font>

553
00:34:48,137 --> 00:34:50,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Learning from a good instructor matters the most...</font>

554
00:34:50,097 --> 00:34:51,637
<font color=#FFFF00>for vocal music students.</font>

555
00:34:51,967 --> 00:34:53,297
<font color=#FFFF00>I think...</font>

556
00:34:54,137 --> 00:34:56,027
<font color=#FFFF00>we should invite a new teacher.</font>

557
00:34:56,167 --> 00:34:57,267
<font color=#FFFF00>Who?</font>

558
00:35:24,827 --> 00:35:27,197
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't seem to put the pieces together.</font>

559
00:35:28,727 --> 00:35:31,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Someone is definitely lying.</font>

560
00:35:36,367 --> 00:35:37,927
<font color=#FFFF00>It's driving me crazy.</font>

561
00:35:49,867 --> 00:35:50,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

562
00:35:54,397 --> 00:35:57,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Hi, my dear daughter. How have you been?</font>

563
00:35:58,897 --> 00:35:59,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Have you been well?</font>

564
00:36:01,097 --> 00:36:04,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I have been well. Aren't you busy though, Dad?</font>

565
00:36:04,497 --> 00:36:07,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course, I am busy,</font>

566
00:36:07,397 --> 00:36:10,067
<font color=#FFFF00>but I came here to give you a present.</font>

567
00:36:10,267 --> 00:36:11,967
<font color=#FFFF00>A present?</font>

568
00:36:14,527 --> 00:36:15,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you like it?</font>

569
00:36:17,137 --> 00:36:18,137
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad!</font>

570
00:36:20,267 --> 00:36:23,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Here you go. This is a shot of espresso you like.</font>

571
00:36:23,597 --> 00:36:24,597
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

572
00:36:27,527 --> 00:36:31,567
<font color=#FFFF00>I noticed that you didn't have a car given your age.</font>

573
00:36:32,467 --> 00:36:35,197
<font color=#FFFF00>I used up all my money when I went to meet you.</font>

574
00:36:36,967 --> 00:36:39,727
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry about that and...</font>

575
00:36:40,727 --> 00:36:42,827
<font color=#FFFF00>thank you for accepting me without giving me a hard time...</font>

576
00:36:43,467 --> 00:36:46,097
<font color=#FFFF00>although I was away for 30 years.</font>

577
00:36:46,767 --> 00:36:47,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

578
00:36:48,027 --> 00:36:51,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't say such things. I told you I am not angry at you.</font>

579
00:36:52,427 --> 00:36:56,367
<font color=#FFFF00>We can talk more later when we have time.</font>

580
00:36:57,227 --> 00:36:58,467
<font color=#FFFF00>See that car over there?</font>

581
00:36:59,897 --> 00:37:01,427
<font color=#FFFF00>- What? - You should...</font>

582
00:37:02,167 --> 00:37:04,927
<font color=#FFFF00>take that car and bring your mother to my concert. Okay?</font>

583
00:37:05,527 --> 00:37:09,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad. You're not giving it to me.</font>

584
00:37:09,497 --> 00:37:11,267
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it to drive around Mom?</font>

585
00:37:11,827 --> 00:37:13,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Look at you. Since you take after Ae Ri,</font>

586
00:37:14,137 --> 00:37:16,637
<font color=#FFFF00>you are quite smart.</font>

587
00:37:17,137 --> 00:37:18,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

588
00:37:21,297 --> 00:37:23,267
<font color=#FFFF00>I really love Ae Ri.</font>

589
00:37:24,267 --> 00:37:27,497
<font color=#FFFF00>I haven't forgotten about her for the last 30 years,</font>

590
00:37:28,667 --> 00:37:29,967
<font color=#FFFF00>but I...</font>

591
00:37:31,227 --> 00:37:34,027
<font color=#FFFF00>might have loved you more than your mother.</font>

592
00:37:34,267 --> 00:37:36,597
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I really want to show her...</font>

593
00:37:37,227 --> 00:37:38,567
<font color=#FFFF00>how much...</font>

594
00:37:39,297 --> 00:37:41,597
<font color=#FFFF00>I loved her while I was away...</font>

595
00:37:41,637 --> 00:37:43,527
<font color=#FFFF00>and how hard I worked.</font>

596
00:37:44,897 --> 00:37:48,997
<font color=#FFFF00>I wonder if I do, perhaps, her anger might subside.</font>

597
00:37:50,497 --> 00:37:53,137
<font color=#FFFF00>- All right. - You understand me, right?</font>

598
00:37:53,867 --> 00:37:55,867
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course, I do.</font>

599
00:37:56,497 --> 00:37:57,997
<font color=#FFFF00>All right. Thank you.</font>

600
00:38:02,927 --> 00:38:05,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad. Don't worry. I will be at your concert for certain.</font>

601
00:38:06,137 --> 00:38:07,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. Bye.</font>

602
00:38:09,997 --> 00:38:11,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Drive carefully.</font>

603
00:38:12,367 --> 00:38:13,467
<font color=#FFFF00>I will.</font>

604
00:38:28,167 --> 00:38:29,927
<font color=#FFFF00>(Seoul Detention Center)</font>

605
00:38:35,327 --> 00:38:37,897
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ms. Yoon. - Jeong Eun.</font>

606
00:38:40,867 --> 00:38:42,467
<font color=#FFFF00>What happened?</font>

607
00:38:42,827 --> 00:38:46,767
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard what happened, but I'd have never guessed you'd end up here.</font>

608
00:38:47,897 --> 00:38:50,667
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't know either.</font>

609
00:39:04,497 --> 00:39:06,097
<font color=#FFFF00>This is all part of my karma.</font>

610
00:39:07,367 --> 00:39:11,527
<font color=#FFFF00>But no one lives in Korea without committing a single illegal act.</font>

611
00:39:12,597 --> 00:39:14,427
<font color=#FFFF00>If you are unlucky, you get caught.</font>

612
00:39:15,497 --> 00:39:18,567
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Yoon. To be frank,</font>

613
00:39:19,427 --> 00:39:22,637
<font color=#FFFF00>I came to talk about the person who put you here.</font>

614
00:39:24,397 --> 00:39:25,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Who do you mean?</font>

615
00:39:27,197 --> 00:39:28,397
<font color=#FFFF00>I mean Mr. Lee.</font>

616
00:39:30,697 --> 00:39:31,797
<font color=#FFFF00>His name is Lee Hyun Woo.</font>

617
00:39:33,197 --> 00:39:34,527
<font color=#FFFF00>What about him?</font>

618
00:39:34,997 --> 00:39:37,867
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard everything.</font>

619
00:39:39,697 --> 00:39:42,667
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard the rumors and what you said.</font>

620
00:39:42,767 --> 00:39:44,497
<font color=#FFFF00>I also checked on my own.</font>

621
00:39:45,367 --> 00:39:48,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Lee is the son of the driver, right?</font>

622
00:39:50,667 --> 00:39:53,137
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. He is.</font>

623
00:40:02,367 --> 00:40:05,097
<font color=#FFFF00>What on earth happened 23 years ago?</font>

624
00:40:06,667 --> 00:40:07,697
<font color=#FFFF00>The truth is...</font>

625
00:40:08,327 --> 00:40:10,767
<font color=#FFFF00>the driver was innocent.</font>

626
00:40:11,367 --> 00:40:12,367
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

627
00:40:13,267 --> 00:40:17,497
<font color=#FFFF00>The accident happened because Guem Ja's bus brakes were old.</font>

628
00:40:18,227 --> 00:40:19,527
<font color=#FFFF00>Then?</font>

629
00:40:20,967 --> 00:40:24,567
<font color=#FFFF00>A lot of students were hurt.</font>

630
00:40:24,727 --> 00:40:26,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Since no one died from it,</font>

631
00:40:26,997 --> 00:40:29,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Guem Ja tried to settle,</font>

632
00:40:29,427 --> 00:40:31,027
<font color=#FFFF00>but your uncle...</font>

633
00:40:31,597 --> 00:40:33,137
<font color=#FFFF00>What did my uncle do?</font>

634
00:40:33,397 --> 00:40:35,827
<font color=#FFFF00>He wanted to get to the bottom of the accident by all means...</font>

635
00:40:35,927 --> 00:40:38,967
<font color=#FFFF00>and insisted that the driver be punished.</font>

636
00:40:40,727 --> 00:40:41,797
<font color=#FFFF00>So then?</font>

637
00:40:42,897 --> 00:40:43,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Eun.</font>

638
00:40:44,667 --> 00:40:47,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Guem Ja, Mi Ja,</font>

639
00:40:47,567 --> 00:40:50,567
<font color=#FFFF00>other parents, and I were going to...</font>

640
00:40:50,667 --> 00:40:52,897
<font color=#FFFF00>settle the accident.</font>

641
00:40:53,867 --> 00:40:56,667
<font color=#FFFF00>Guem Ja even came up with the settlement.</font>

642
00:40:57,137 --> 00:40:58,767
<font color=#FFFF00>However, your uncle...</font>

643
00:41:00,927 --> 00:41:03,497
<font color=#FFFF00>He was literarily jumping up and down out of anger.</font>

644
00:41:03,597 --> 00:41:05,637
<font color=#FFFF00>We weren't able to stop him.</font>

645
00:41:06,897 --> 00:41:08,137
<font color=#FFFF00>Guem Ja said...</font>

646
00:41:08,697 --> 00:41:10,767
<font color=#FFFF00>if she become criminally liable for the accident,</font>

647
00:41:11,227 --> 00:41:13,267
<font color=#FFFF00>her academy would be in ruins.</font>

648
00:41:14,197 --> 00:41:15,327
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why...</font>

649
00:41:17,137 --> 00:41:21,227
<font color=#FFFF00>she framed the driver and blamed it on his drunk driving.</font>

650
00:41:22,927 --> 00:41:25,167
<font color=#FFFF00>I helped her to frame him.</font>

651
00:41:26,997 --> 00:41:28,797
<font color=#FFFF00>He was known...</font>

652
00:41:29,027 --> 00:41:31,697
<font color=#FFFF00>to be an alcoholic in the neighborhood.</font>

653
00:41:31,827 --> 00:41:35,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Yoon. How could you do such a thing?</font>

654
00:41:36,067 --> 00:41:38,367
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you frame an innocent man?</font>

655
00:41:38,397 --> 00:41:40,167
<font color=#FFFF00>We didn't want to.</font>

656
00:41:40,867 --> 00:41:43,567
<font color=#FFFF00>It was your uncle who hinted that...</font>

657
00:41:43,567 --> 00:41:45,197
<font color=#FFFF00>he might have driven drunk.</font>

658
00:41:46,227 --> 00:41:49,327
<font color=#FFFF00>He wanted him to take a sobriety test since he was an alcoholic.</font>

659
00:41:49,897 --> 00:41:53,027
<font color=#FFFF00>He even said he'd sue Guem Ja for hiring such an unfit driver.</font>

660
00:41:54,097 --> 00:41:57,767
<font color=#FFFF00>How was she supposed to handle your uncle when he went berserk.</font>

661
00:41:59,427 --> 00:42:01,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Instead of both of them going down for the accident,</font>

662
00:42:02,097 --> 00:42:03,667
<font color=#FFFF00>she thought one person would be enough.</font>

663
00:42:06,667 --> 00:42:08,797
<font color=#FFFF00>This can't be true. Even if it was true...</font>

664
00:42:08,827 --> 00:42:11,897
<font color=#FFFF00>It is true. Now your uncle has become soft.</font>

665
00:42:12,197 --> 00:42:15,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Given his old character, this isn't out of his character.</font>

666
00:42:17,997 --> 00:42:21,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Out of all people, how could a son of the driver return?</font>

667
00:42:22,997 --> 00:42:25,167
<font color=#FFFF00>He even returned to his old neighborhood.</font>

668
00:42:26,897 --> 00:42:28,897
<font color=#FFFF00>I felt awful and terrified.</font>

669
00:42:29,227 --> 00:42:30,827
<font color=#FFFF00>I'd rather be here.</font>

670
00:42:34,827 --> 00:42:36,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Does my uncle...</font>

671
00:42:36,827 --> 00:42:39,467
<font color=#FFFF00>- know about this? - No, he doesn't.</font>

672
00:42:39,897 --> 00:42:42,827
<font color=#FFFF00>It's been a lifetime secret between Guem Ja and me.</font>

673
00:42:43,067 --> 00:42:44,637
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Yoon.</font>

674
00:42:44,867 --> 00:42:47,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you do that?</font>

675
00:42:48,367 --> 00:42:49,397
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way,</font>

676
00:42:50,967 --> 00:42:52,867
<font color=#FFFF00>how is your uncle's family?</font>

677
00:42:54,197 --> 00:42:57,867
<font color=#FFFF00>I bet Mr. Lee won't leave your uncle's family alone.</font>

678
00:43:00,137 --> 00:43:01,427
<font color=#FFFF00>(David Lee, President of Golden Street)</font>

679
00:43:01,427 --> 00:43:03,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello. This is Han Jeong Hwa.</font>

680
00:43:03,997 --> 00:43:05,637
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you for yesterday.</font>

681
00:43:05,867 --> 00:43:09,227
<font color=#FFFF00>I'd like to buy you a cup of tea. How about now?</font>

682
00:43:12,927 --> 00:43:14,067
<font color=#FFFF00>You're already here.</font>

683
00:43:16,167 --> 00:43:17,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Where would you like to go?</font>

684
00:43:18,427 --> 00:43:20,067
<font color=#FFFF00>I will take you to a place I have in mind.</font>

685
00:43:21,097 --> 00:43:22,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Sounds great.</font>

686
00:44:03,697 --> 00:44:04,897
<font color=#FFFF00>(Mom)</font>

687
00:44:12,597 --> 00:44:14,827
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes, Mom. - What's up with you?</font>

688
00:44:14,897 --> 00:44:17,297
<font color=#FFFF00>You said you wanted to have dinner together. Where have you gone?</font>

689
00:44:17,297 --> 00:44:19,767
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry, Mom. What time is it?</font>

690
00:44:19,797 --> 00:44:21,927
<font color=#FFFF00>It's 6'o clock. What's going on?</font>

691
00:44:22,567 --> 00:44:25,867
<font color=#FFFF00>I expected to have dinner together and yet, you're making me wait?</font>

692
00:44:26,297 --> 00:44:28,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. This is so like you.</font>

693
00:44:29,067 --> 00:44:30,897
<font color=#FFFF00>I will be there soon. Come out of the house.</font>

694
00:44:31,527 --> 00:44:33,727
<font color=#FFFF00>- I will pick you up with my car. - With your car?</font>

695
00:44:34,097 --> 00:44:35,167
<font color=#FFFF00>You have a car?</font>

696
00:44:37,427 --> 00:44:39,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. Why do you have a car?</font>

697
00:44:40,267 --> 00:44:43,267
<font color=#FFFF00>Ta-da! Starting today, I have a car.</font>

698
00:44:43,397 --> 00:44:46,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Is someone getting married? What is this ribbon doing here?</font>

699
00:44:46,397 --> 00:44:48,997
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with it? It's pretty.</font>

700
00:44:49,097 --> 00:44:50,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you buy this?</font>

701
00:44:50,927 --> 00:44:52,967
<font color=#FFFF00>- A guy gave this to me. - Who?</font>

702
00:44:53,167 --> 00:44:54,767
<font color=#FFFF00>This guy is new.</font>

703
00:44:56,667 --> 00:44:58,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Right. Get in. We're late.</font>

704
00:44:59,997 --> 00:45:01,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Please get in.</font>

705
00:45:13,227 --> 00:45:15,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are we going to eat?</font>

706
00:45:16,397 --> 00:45:17,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Wear the seatbelt.</font>

707
00:45:18,667 --> 00:45:19,667
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom,</font>

708
00:45:19,997 --> 00:45:22,567
<font color=#FFFF00>do we have to eat on a day like this?</font>

709
00:45:22,727 --> 00:45:24,427
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you talking about?</font>

710
00:45:24,797 --> 00:45:26,997
<font color=#FFFF00>You said you're taking me out.</font>

711
00:45:27,127 --> 00:45:29,527
<font color=#FFFF00>I wanted to be treated by my daughter.</font>

712
00:45:29,867 --> 00:45:33,197
<font color=#FFFF00>There's something much more important than food.</font>

713
00:45:33,197 --> 00:45:34,497
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

714
00:45:34,797 --> 00:45:35,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go.</font>

715
00:45:39,927 --> 00:45:43,997
<font color=#FFFF00>(Bariton Ryu Myung Jin's Concert)</font>

716
00:45:45,597 --> 00:45:46,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you bring me here?</font>

717
00:45:48,167 --> 00:45:51,327
<font color=#FFFF00>This is what's more important than food.</font>

718
00:45:59,797 --> 00:46:01,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom, hurry up.</font>

719
00:46:01,527 --> 00:46:02,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

720
00:46:06,297 --> 00:46:08,027
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?</font>

721
00:46:09,667 --> 00:46:11,067
<font color=#FFFF00>After the concert,</font>

722
00:46:12,667 --> 00:46:16,167
<font color=#FFFF00>we can eat with Dad. All three of us together.</font>

723
00:46:16,167 --> 00:46:17,767
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jeong Eun. - Mom.</font>

724
00:46:18,067 --> 00:46:20,067
<font color=#FFFF00>I am 31 years old, and I have never eaten...</font>

725
00:46:20,067 --> 00:46:23,267
<font color=#FFFF00>a meal with my parents. I'm such a pitiful person.</font>

726
00:46:23,367 --> 00:46:25,267
<font color=#FFFF00>They say you never know who will die first.</font>

727
00:46:25,367 --> 00:46:27,567
<font color=#FFFF00>Please cut me a slack...</font>

728
00:46:27,567 --> 00:46:29,467
<font color=#FFFF00>in case I might die before you. Okay?</font>

729
00:46:29,867 --> 00:46:31,827
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't let this one pass.</font>

730
00:46:31,867 --> 00:46:33,697
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mom. - Let go of me!</font>

731
00:46:33,967 --> 00:46:35,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

732
00:46:36,667 --> 00:46:37,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom,</font>

733
00:46:38,427 --> 00:46:39,697
<font color=#FFFF00>you know those people, right?</font>

734
00:46:40,997 --> 00:46:42,627
<font color=#FFFF00>They are the people from the music industry.</font>

735
00:46:42,967 --> 00:46:44,727
<font color=#FFFF00>They know both you and Dad.</font>

736
00:46:45,067 --> 00:46:48,027
<font color=#FFFF00>You are famous, and Dad is even more famous.</font>

737
00:46:48,567 --> 00:46:49,567
<font color=#FFFF00>So what?</font>

738
00:46:49,867 --> 00:46:53,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's appear cool and fabulous.</font>

739
00:46:54,567 --> 00:46:56,127
<font color=#FFFF00>You will get embarrassed if they see you like this.</font>

740
00:46:57,197 --> 00:46:59,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Act like a Hollywood couple who are cool with each other...</font>

741
00:46:59,167 --> 00:47:01,027
<font color=#FFFF00>after the divorce.</font>

742
00:47:01,367 --> 00:47:03,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go inside like one of them.</font>

743
00:47:03,197 --> 00:47:05,927
<font color=#FFFF00>We are nothing like a Hollywood couple.</font>

744
00:47:06,727 --> 00:47:07,867
<font color=#FFFF00>- Gosh. - You are the Hollywood star.</font>

745
00:47:09,967 --> 00:47:10,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go.</font>

746
00:47:13,297 --> 00:47:14,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on, Mom.</font>

747
00:47:36,867 --> 00:47:37,867
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo,</font>

748
00:47:38,367 --> 00:47:39,627
<font color=#FFFF00>this is the place.</font>

749
00:47:40,867 --> 00:47:41,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, Mom.</font>

750
00:47:42,327 --> 00:47:44,897
<font color=#FFFF00>He is world-famous baritone...</font>

751
00:47:45,067 --> 00:47:46,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Korea ever gave birth to.</font>

752
00:47:49,297 --> 00:47:53,067
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes. - Watching his performance will...</font>

753
00:47:53,697 --> 00:47:55,997
<font color=#FFFF00>make you a world-renowned opera singer.</font>

754
00:47:56,527 --> 00:47:57,967
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I paid...</font>

755
00:47:59,897 --> 00:48:03,527
<font color=#FFFF00>an unbelievably high price...</font>

756
00:48:05,327 --> 00:48:07,297
<font color=#FFFF00>to buy these tickets for you.</font>

757
00:48:07,497 --> 00:48:08,767
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you, Mom.</font>

758
00:48:09,727 --> 00:48:10,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Shall we go in, Chang Soo?</font>

759
00:48:11,967 --> 00:48:12,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

760
00:48:19,697 --> 00:48:21,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Here are the tickets.</font>

761
00:48:25,327 --> 00:48:26,927
<font color=#FFFF00>People are going in. Hurry up.</font>

762
00:48:27,067 --> 00:48:28,527
<font color=#FFFF00>It's going to start.</font>

763
00:48:29,597 --> 00:48:32,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go.</font>

764
00:48:33,267 --> 00:48:34,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Here are the tickets.</font>

765
00:48:34,727 --> 00:48:35,767
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

766
00:48:51,067 --> 00:48:53,027
<font color=#FFFF00>You get it now, don't you?</font>

767
00:49:19,527 --> 00:49:22,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom, why don't you take off your sunglasses?</font>

768
00:49:22,997 --> 00:49:25,027
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want to see your dad's face.</font>

769
00:49:25,227 --> 00:49:27,227
<font color=#FFFF00>We came here to hear his singing, not to see his face.</font>

770
00:49:27,897 --> 00:49:30,697
<font color=#FFFF00>You are unbelievable, Mom.</font>

771
00:50:12,867 --> 00:50:14,067
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

772
00:50:15,367 --> 00:50:17,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you for coming...</font>

773
00:50:18,267 --> 00:50:20,997
<font color=#FFFF00>to watch my humble concert.</font>

774
00:50:27,767 --> 00:50:31,367
<font color=#FFFF00>I've dedicated my life to music,</font>

775
00:50:32,367 --> 00:50:34,967
