<font color=#FFFF00>there is nothing else I can do but sing, and...</font>

778
00:50:41,097 --> 00:50:44,997
<font color=#FFFF00>it sometimes makes me embarrassed and sometimes makes me proud.</font>

779
00:50:49,627 --> 00:50:52,497
<font color=#FFFF00>What a joke.</font>

780
00:50:52,567 --> 00:50:54,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell him to sing one more song.</font>

