00:50:55,567 --> 00:50:57,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

782
00:50:57,467 --> 00:50:58,797
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?</font>

783
00:50:58,927 --> 00:51:00,997
<font color=#FFFF00>There is just one thing...</font>

