00:51:02,267 --> 00:51:03,697
<font color=#FFFF00>I regret.</font>

785
00:51:04,327 --> 00:51:07,497
<font color=#FFFF00>I hurt the woman...</font>

786
00:51:08,227 --> 00:51:10,497
<font color=#FFFF00>who waited for me.</font>

