828
00:54:33,397 --> 00:54:38,397
<font color=#FFFF00>there's something I can help you with.</font>

829
00:54:43,797 --> 00:54:45,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui is determined.</font>

830
00:54:46,097 --> 00:54:47,967
<font color=#FFFF00>Her computer might get set on fire.</font>

831
00:54:47,967 --> 00:54:51,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Her pride must've been hurt. She failed on her first try.</font>

832
00:54:51,227 --> 00:54:53,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui, you can do well this time, right?</font>

833
00:54:53,567 --> 00:54:55,367
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, of course. I can do well.</font>

834
00:54:55,867 --> 00:54:59,197
<font color=#FFFF00>Why is she so confident?</font>

835
00:54:59,497 --> 00:55:01,827
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui, have you done...</font>

836
00:55:01,827 --> 00:55:03,197
<font color=#FFFF00>the survey for the yoga and Pilates line?</font>

837
00:55:03,197 --> 00:55:04,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Most professionals liked them.</font>

838
00:55:04,897 --> 00:55:08,167
<font color=#FFFF00>They like the design and the excellent elasticity.</font>

839
00:55:08,367 --> 00:55:10,167
<font color=#FFFF00>The report is on your desk.</font>

840
00:55:11,067 --> 00:55:12,727
<font color=#FFFF00>How is it received among the age groups?</font>

841
00:55:12,727 --> 00:55:15,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Our target age groups, the 20s and 30s are most receptive.</font>

842
00:55:15,397 --> 00:55:16,927
<font color=#FFFF00>The moving studio will open...</font>

843
00:55:16,927 --> 00:55:20,227
<font color=#FFFF00>in Konkuk University Station where there will be a younger clientele.</font>

844
00:55:20,497 --> 00:55:23,697
<font color=#FFFF00>The report regarding this matter is on your desk as well.</font>

845
00:55:24,197 --> 00:55:26,867
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with you, Dong Hui? Are you sick?</font>

846
00:55:26,867 --> 00:55:30,027
<font color=#FFFF00>She's not sick. She's angry that she lost to Writer Choi.</font>

847
00:55:30,797 --> 00:55:32,567
<font color=#FFFF00>She is sick with anger.</font>

848
00:55:33,227 --> 00:55:35,997
<font color=#FFFF00>I really hope you win this time, Dong Hui.</font>

849
00:55:36,127 --> 00:55:40,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you survey reactions towards the competing company's new products?</font>

850
00:55:40,697 --> 00:55:42,827
<font color=#FFFF00>I did. I did everything.</font>

851
00:55:42,897 --> 00:55:44,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Please just look at your desk.</font>

852
00:55:45,997 --> 00:55:49,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you see the way she looked at me? I can't believe this.</font>

853
00:55:51,027 --> 00:55:52,767
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hello. Director. - Hi. Director.</font>

854
00:55:55,967 --> 00:55:57,967
<font color=#FFFF00>- What are you doing, Ms. Oh? - Pardon?</font>

855
00:55:58,397 --> 00:56:00,667
<font color=#FFFF00>She's writing next episode's script.</font>

856
00:56:01,327 --> 00:56:04,867
<font color=#FFFF00>She finished all her given assignments. I just checked.</font>

857
00:56:05,967 --> 00:56:08,167
<font color=#FFFF00>You are writing next episode's script?</font>

858
00:56:08,597 --> 00:56:09,767
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I am.</font>

859
00:56:10,527 --> 00:56:12,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Didn't Director Han inform you?</font>

860
00:56:13,467 --> 00:56:14,567
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

861
00:56:15,727 --> 00:56:17,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello, Director.</font>

862
00:56:18,097 --> 00:56:19,897
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Bang. Can we have a word?</font>

863
00:56:34,627 --> 00:56:36,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Didn't you get the message yet?</font>

864
00:56:37,327 --> 00:56:40,627
<font color=#FFFF00>- What message? - She'll no longer write scripts.</font>

865
00:56:42,997 --> 00:56:44,197
<font color=#FFFF00>How did you find out?</font>

866
00:56:44,397 --> 00:56:46,597
<font color=#FFFF00>How? I heard it from President Lee.</font>

867
00:56:48,327 --> 00:56:51,997
<font color=#FFFF00>I am going to try to persuade President Lee. Don't tell her yet.</font>

868
00:56:52,197 --> 00:56:55,227
<font color=#FFFF00>Why? Han Seong Joon. Are you serious?</font>

869
00:56:55,667 --> 00:56:58,497
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you dragging this out? How much help can she be?</font>

870
00:56:58,667 --> 00:57:01,797
<font color=#FFFF00>When she finishes the scripts, we'll end up using Writer Choi's scripts.</font>

871
00:57:01,867 --> 00:57:04,867
<font color=#FFFF00>If we continue with this, we are sacrificing our resources...</font>

872
00:57:04,867 --> 00:57:06,967
<font color=#FFFF00>to help her gain experience and earn money.</font>

873
00:57:07,327 --> 00:57:10,197
<font color=#FFFF00>President Lee agreed on this. That's why he called you in.</font>

874
00:57:12,527 --> 00:57:14,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are they fighting so much?</font>

875
00:57:15,927 --> 00:57:17,497
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it about the scripts again?</font>

876
00:57:20,797 --> 00:57:23,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you talk to President Lee about this?</font>

877
00:57:23,727 --> 00:57:27,067
<font color=#FFFF00>No, he called me first and told me this himself.</font>

878
00:57:28,827 --> 00:57:31,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't look at me like that. I don't play games.</font>

879
00:57:32,627 --> 00:57:33,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Then it's fine.</font>

880
00:57:34,497 --> 00:57:35,997
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you going to do?</font>

881
00:57:36,967 --> 00:57:40,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Whatever it takes, I will convince President Lee.</font>

882
00:57:40,397 --> 00:57:41,827
<font color=#FFFF00>You should do whatever you want to do.</font>

883
00:57:42,097 --> 00:57:44,227
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean that I should do whatever I want to do?</font>

884
00:57:45,467 --> 00:57:47,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't pick at my words. I am tired.</font>

885
00:57:47,597 --> 00:57:48,867
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

886
00:57:49,297 --> 00:57:51,627
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you please leave? I'm exhausted.</font>

887
00:57:53,897 --> 00:57:55,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Go home and focus on your writing.</font>

888
00:57:56,827 --> 00:57:58,067
<font color=#FFFF00>She's right.</font>

889
00:57:58,497 --> 00:58:01,567
<font color=#FFFF00>You got too many assignments from the Marketing Department.</font>

890
00:58:01,567 --> 00:58:03,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't say that.</font>

891
00:58:03,297 --> 00:58:06,167
<font color=#FFFF00>I also hope that she would succeed as a writer.</font>

892
00:58:06,167 --> 00:58:09,067
<font color=#FFFF00>That's how she will keep giving me soybean paste and red chili paste.</font>

893
00:58:09,627 --> 00:58:12,867
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry about that. I will continue to provide with those.</font>

894
00:58:13,567 --> 00:58:16,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, how can you be so easily bribed?</font>

895
00:58:16,467 --> 00:58:19,127
<font color=#FFFF00>My point is you should write as if today is your last day alive.</font>

896
00:58:19,227 --> 00:58:20,227
<font color=#FFFF00>I will.</font>

897
00:58:26,727 --> 00:58:28,367
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hello, President. - Hello, President.</font>

898
00:58:28,367 --> 00:58:30,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Hi. Are you going home now?</font>

899
00:58:30,527 --> 00:58:32,327
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes, Sir. - Yes, Sir.</font>

900
00:58:34,367 --> 00:58:37,667
<font color=#FFFF00>Look who's here. Aren't you Dong Hui?</font>

901
00:58:37,997 --> 00:58:40,327
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yes, President. - All right.</font>

902
00:58:41,067 --> 00:58:43,767
<font color=#FFFF00>- Are you going home too? - Yes, I am.</font>

903
00:58:44,267 --> 00:58:45,297
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

904
00:58:46,067 --> 00:58:48,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom. I am home.</font>

905
00:58:48,497 --> 00:58:49,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Gwang Jin is here.</font>

906
00:58:51,097 --> 00:58:54,527
<font color=#FFFF00>Although it was so sudden, I did try to prepare something for the guest.</font>

907
00:58:54,567 --> 00:58:56,597
<font color=#FFFF00>I wonder if this will be to the guest's liking or not.</font>

908
00:59:02,027 --> 00:59:03,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

909
00:59:04,427 --> 00:59:05,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

910
00:59:40,497 --> 00:59:41,497
<font color=#FFFF00>Who is it?</font>

911
00:59:43,167 --> 00:59:44,767
<font color=#FFFF00>It's Han Seong Joon across the street.</font>

912
00:59:48,367 --> 00:59:49,467
<font color=#FFFF00>You're visiting me often now.</font>

913
00:59:52,567 --> 00:59:55,027
<font color=#FFFF00>- Would you like a drink? - Yes.</font>

914
00:59:56,097 --> 00:59:57,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Come in.</font>

915
01:00:04,967 --> 01:00:07,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you take out the ice?</font>

916
01:00:07,697 --> 01:00:08,697
<font color=#FFFF00>All right.</font>

917
01:00:22,527 --> 01:00:23,567
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

918
01:00:23,927 --> 01:00:26,467
<font color=#FFFF00>It feels more friendly to see you in my kitchen.</font>

919
01:00:29,097 --> 01:00:30,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Here you go.</font>

920
01:00:33,297 --> 01:00:35,867
<font color=#FFFF00>If you were my brother, we could have...</font>

921
01:00:36,627 --> 01:00:39,867
<font color=#FFFF00>eaten ramyeon together, Couldn't we have?</font>

922
01:00:43,567 --> 01:00:44,827
<font color=#FFFF00>I am just joking.</font>

923
01:00:46,827 --> 01:00:49,667
<font color=#FFFF00>If we become too friendly, it will interfere with our business.</font>

924
01:00:50,197 --> 01:00:51,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go to the living room.</font>

925
01:01:02,327 --> 01:01:04,967
<font color=#FFFF00>All right. So what do you want to talk about?</font>

926
01:01:05,367 --> 01:01:07,067
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't let go of Writer Oh Dong Hui.</font>

927
01:01:08,967 --> 01:01:11,527
<font color=#FFFF00>This is so like you.</font>

928
01:01:11,867 --> 01:01:13,727
<font color=#FFFF00>I am not running a business.</font>

929
01:01:13,767 --> 01:01:17,697
<font color=#FFFF00>I am not making a product but a work of art and cultural art.</font>

930
01:01:18,467 --> 01:01:22,127
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why the crew members including writers aren't...</font>

931
01:01:22,127 --> 01:01:25,567
<font color=#FFFF00>pieces of tools. We are colleagues producing a work of art together.</font>

932
01:01:25,727 --> 01:01:29,597
<font color=#FFFF00>They're not pieces that I can change because they are not adequate.</font>

933
01:01:33,127 --> 01:01:35,397
<font color=#FFFF00>You are the worst as a businessman.</font>

934
01:01:35,967 --> 01:01:39,327
<font color=#FFFF00>Whether it was kindness or hostility towards me that made you invest,</font>

935
01:01:39,527 --> 01:01:41,227
<font color=#FFFF00>if you invested because you believed in my ability,</font>

936
01:01:41,327 --> 01:01:43,667
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope you can continue to trust my decisions.</font>

937
01:01:43,967 --> 01:01:47,467
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope you would give Writer Oh at least a chance to redeem herself.</font>

938
01:01:50,197 --> 01:01:52,097
<font color=#FFFF00>What is the reason I have to trust your decisions?</font>

939
01:01:52,767 --> 01:01:54,167
<font color=#FFFF00>I say this with respect.</font>

940
01:01:54,797 --> 01:01:56,627
<font color=#FFFF00>I would like to appeal to your emotion.</font>

941
01:01:57,097 --> 01:02:00,467
<font color=#FFFF00>Please consider me as your brother and give me another chance.</font>

942
01:02:03,167 --> 01:02:06,767
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think what you just said is rude?</font>

943
01:02:08,297 --> 01:02:11,927
<font color=#FFFF00>I certainly told you that my brother is dead.</font>

944
01:02:12,567 --> 01:02:15,667
<font color=#FFFF00>I am too desperate that I am willing to be rude.</font>

945
01:02:19,667 --> 01:02:22,297
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you like her that much?</font>

946
01:02:24,697 --> 01:02:27,097
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you asking me about my personal feelings?</font>

947
01:02:29,127 --> 01:02:32,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Can I ask? Just like an older brother asking his younger brother.</font>

948
01:02:34,997 --> 01:02:37,867
<font color=#FFFF00>I love her very much.</font>

949
01:02:39,527 --> 01:02:43,367
<font color=#FFFF00>How about you? Have you ever loved anyone?</font>

950
01:02:44,467 --> 01:02:47,197
<font color=#FFFF00>I am not certain. I've never...</font>

951
01:02:48,227 --> 01:02:50,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, I might have loved once or twice.</font>

952
01:02:53,897 --> 01:02:57,097
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't have time, for I've looked for my brother my whole life.</font>

953
01:02:58,927 --> 01:03:02,327
<font color=#FFFF00>I've never rested, loved anyone,</font>

954
01:03:02,867 --> 01:03:04,427
<font color=#FFFF00>or gone on trips.</font>

955
01:03:04,967 --> 01:03:06,367
<font color=#FFFF00>I only worked...</font>

956
01:03:07,627 --> 01:03:09,197
<font color=#FFFF00>to find my brother.</font>

957
01:03:12,027 --> 01:03:14,797
<font color=#FFFF00>In a way, I've only loved him...</font>

958
01:03:15,067 --> 01:03:16,927
<font color=#FFFF00>and looked for him my entire life.</font>

959
01:03:18,927 --> 01:03:19,927
<font color=#FFFF00>Although the result...</font>

960
01:03:22,927 --> 01:03:24,867
<font color=#FFFF00>is too miserable.</font>

961
01:03:35,027 --> 01:03:36,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

962
01:03:37,597 --> 01:03:38,797
<font color=#FFFF00>You should leave.</font>

963
01:03:40,167 --> 01:03:41,897
<font color=#FFFF00>I am cold-hearted by nature.</font>

964
01:03:42,267 --> 01:03:45,027
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't intend to get involved in someone's love life.</font>

965
01:03:45,927 --> 01:03:47,797
<font color=#FFFF00>So you should leave now.</font>

966
01:03:50,727 --> 01:03:51,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir.</font>

967
01:03:59,697 --> 01:04:00,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

968
01:04:10,997 --> 01:04:13,627
<font color=#FFFF00>If I may, may I ask who this is?</font>

969
01:04:15,397 --> 01:04:16,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do you ask?</font>

970
01:04:19,727 --> 01:04:20,727
<font color=#FFFF00>Just because.</font>

971
01:04:23,627 --> 01:04:26,097
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm seeing a lot of new sides of you tonight.</font>

972
01:04:30,167 --> 01:04:32,427
<font color=#FFFF00>That's my brother when he was young.</font>

973
01:04:34,797 --> 01:04:35,797
<font color=#FFFF00>Does it answer your question?</font>

974
01:04:37,727 --> 01:04:38,727
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

975
01:04:59,897 --> 01:05:01,567
<font color=#FFFF00>(Father, I'll Take Care of You)</font>

976
01:05:01,867 --> 01:05:04,297
<font color=#FFFF00>How serious are you and Seong Joon?</font>

977
01:05:05,097 --> 01:05:06,527
<font color=#FFFF00>How involved are you with him?</font>

978
01:05:09,127 --> 01:05:10,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you okay?</font>

979
01:05:11,778 --> 01:05:13,448
<font color=#FFFF00>You're a naughty man.</font>

980
01:05:13,897 --> 01:05:15,697
<font color=#FFFF00>Last night, he told me...</font>

981
01:05:16,097 --> 01:05:18,627
<font color=#FFFF00>that his brother is dead.</font>

982
01:05:18,967 --> 01:05:20,167
<font color=#FFFF00>Didn't you hear me?</font>

983
01:05:20,167 --> 01:05:22,427
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyung Seop drove your father...</font>

984
01:05:22,527 --> 01:05:23,967
<font color=#FFFF00>to death.</font>

985
01:05:24,467 --> 01:05:26,797
<font color=#FFFF00>One more thing. It's about Seong Joon.</font>

